{"tid":756550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張炳良：出事就要官員問責下台好消極　指社會看法單純","createTime":"2018-07-26T06:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T16:37:59.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4d46ad9bd3e67b17b4aa17b7645923a2b7a22a86","tid":756550,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180726/s00001/50399566cac955b693c6eed9027f7351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180726%2Fs00001%2F50399566cac955b693c6eed9027f7351.jpg&h=f2d1aca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每當政策、監管出問題，社會都有聲音要求官員履行問責制下台。不過，前運輸及房屋局長張炳良表示，如果有事發生時就要有人「引咎辭職」，是十分消極看法，因涉及的可能是「結構性」問題。他又說，因政制停滯不前，政府行政機關認受性「好脆弱」，令施政舉步維艱。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良早上於商台節目談及問責制，指一旦強調「問責」，而社會對問責這事情看得比較單純，認為一有事情發生，就要官員下台，但設立問責制最終追求的，並非有事發生時就要有人「引咎辭職」、「人頭落地」，「如果這樣是好消極看法。（人頭）落地之後問題仍在這裏。如果問題好結構性，誰人做都是落地」。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良又說，問責制在國際上定義廣闊，「政策範疇發生任何事都可以問責&hellip;&hellip;如果香港是這樣，個個局長都可能隨時引咎辭職」。他認為，問責制一定要配合整個政制進一步改革發展，稱因為政制停滯不前，政府行政機關認受性「好脆弱」，推行政策時舉步維艱。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良另提到，他2012年任局長時，原本希望只負責房屋範疇，「運輸我只是看着，將來會拆（運輸及房屋分拆成兩個局）」，但後來改組不成，而2013年出現高鐵延誤超支問題後，愈來愈多時間花在交通範疇，不斷要「拆彈」和「救火」。<br />\n<br />\n至於房屋問題，張炳良指要多管齊下。他又說，填海雖然不能解決短期問題，惟若現時不決定，中長期便沒有土地供應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180726/s00001/1532575215120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180726%2Fs00001%2F1532575215120&d=OVBuK%2BeWhGt9hbVL8e0DLG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e8b5a0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180726%2Fs00001%2F1532575215120&h=0beb0eab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180726/s00001/1532575215120</a>"},{"pid":"110518b8ab4613af09c66913787bc44f776877ae","tid":756550,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bernard_Picart_-_The_Perfumer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3ABernard_Picart_-_The_Perfumer.jpg&h=c26c382d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7dbd83e29406b93dd049fdd0a255232b597f032","tid":756550,"uid":122,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"咁扣人工<br />\n柒一次扣2成"},{"pid":"e0a1ef103fdb15f5891012c1f01fd6fe9d468023","tid":756550,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"唔落台咪等天誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/152254_b5cf67c0a59eb877032fbc75cb48b403.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F152254_b5cf67c0a59eb877032fbc75cb48b403.png&h=03c6859b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42e85b26551c49a68e1da204b78de347c9649ab8","tid":756550,"uid":72621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"問責制"},{"pid":"01b5d7e7100e050a961db860e9e580559bd8d2c4","tid":756550,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"所以果d咩假奶粉最後都係比人放生哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed85efdad8bce05e0d02a65fc252c0fa5ea81e0","tid":756550,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"OK，唔問責制，<br />\n公投落唔落台好嗎？"},{"pid":"3358f19c83ccb34fba889a993d81a956f39fbf07","tid":756550,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩問責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524e910a23f218b7f017178567e1f9d4ee323ccf","tid":756550,"uid":177590,"like":1,